<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/211550-i-used-this-poem-in-my-spiritual-retreats">I used this poem in my spiritual retreats and workshops at least 18 years ago. Back then there was only a one sheet that showed up in my life (don&#39;t remember how or who gave it to me back then)

I always loved this and found it to be profound and powerful.
Wonder what else in in the book/</a>
</div>
