<span id="freeTextContainer17556336269540592420">The original prose poem is a powerful stand-alone product, but this book that accompanies the original poem is not as compelling. There are nuggets of good moments, and the writing is done well, but some of the ideas are too &quot;in the clouds&quot; and needed some grounding in reality.</span>
  <span id="freeText17556336269540592420" style="display:none">The original prose poem is a powerful stand-alone product, but this book that accompanies the original poem is not as compelling. There are nuggets of good moments, and the writing is done well, but some of the ideas are too "in the clouds" and needed some grounding in reality.</span>
